		<title>BrainStation Launches New Miami Tech Scholarship</title>
		<link>https://brainstation.io/blog/brainstation-launches-new-miami-tech-scholarship</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 02 Sep 2021 17:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Salvatore Ciolfi]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[BrainStation News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Miami]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[scholarships]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://brainstation.io/blog/?p=12885</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>We are proud to introduce the new Miami Tech Scholarship, providing Floridians with up to $5,000 in education funding. </p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog/brainstation-launches-new-miami-tech-scholarship">BrainStation Launches New Miami Tech Scholarship</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog">BrainStation® Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p><em>Global leader in digital skills training now offering $5,000 scholarships toward bootcamps in UX design and web development, increasing access to cutting-edge digital skills training for the future of work.&nbsp;</em><br></p>



<p>Miami, FL &#8212; BrainStation, the global leader in digital skills training, has expanded its industry-leading scholarship program with a new <em>Miami Tech Scholarship</em>, providing aspiring tech professionals in Florida with up to $5,000 in education funding.&nbsp;</p>



<p>All Florida residents are eligible to apply for the <em>Miami Tech Scholarship</em>, which<em> </em>is designed to support the burgeoning Miami tech sector by increasing access to BrainStation’s award-winning bootcamps in UX design, web development and software engineering.&nbsp;</p>



<p>“Since 2012, BrainStation has awarded more than $2 million in scholarship funding, empowering thousands of professionals around the world with digital skills training,” said Johana Mikkola, VP and General Manager of BrainStation Miami. “We’re very proud and excited to be expanding our successful scholarship program into Florida and Miami, which has one of the fastest-growing and most dynamic tech ecosystems in the world. The sky is truly the limit when it comes to Miami tech and we want to be able to support that growth.”    </p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://brainstation.io/book-call"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-1024x551.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-12888" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-1024x551.jpg 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-300x162.jpg 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-768x413.jpg 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-1536x827.jpg 1536w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-2048x1103.jpg 2048w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1-960x517.jpg 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02133545/Quote-Card-Miami-Tech-Scholarship-V1.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<p>Miami’s tech industry has turned into a new global hub for the digital economy over the last few years, and it continues to grow rapidly. Demand for digital skills, however, remains greater than the supply of qualified employees, and that skills gap is growing. In fact, the World Economic Forum estimates that emerging technologies will generate 133 million new jobs in the next year, with more than half of all employees requiring significant reskilling.</p>



<p>To prepare the workforce for these opportunities, BrainStation offers part-time and full-time bootcamps, both online and in-person at its campuses in Miami, New York, London, and Toronto, among others. Over 90% of BrainStation graduates find employment within six months of graduation, with the company providing access to an exclusive hiring network and ongoing career guidance and support, including resume writing and job applications, personal branding, interview preparation, and more.&nbsp;</p>



<p>For more information about BrainStation’s Miami Tech Scholarship, <a href="https://brainstation.io/book-call">please speak to a Learning Advisor</a>.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog/brainstation-launches-new-miami-tech-scholarship">BrainStation Launches New Miami Tech Scholarship</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog">BrainStation® Blog</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
