<p>The&nbsp;<a href="https://brainstation.io/scholarships?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=EYScholarshipJune22"><em>EY Women in Technology</em>&nbsp;<em>Scholarship</em></a> reduces barriers for the many talented, ambitious women looking to pursue a digital career.&nbsp;</p>



