								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>We are excited to announce that CourseCompare has named BrainStation the <a href="https://www.coursecompare.ca/best-coding-bootcamps/?utm_source=BSTNblog&amp;utm_medium=blog_CourseCompare&amp;utm_campaign=WD_BestCodingBootcamp">Best Coding Bootcamp for 2021</a>.</p>



<p>CourseCompare is a leading marketplace for digital education, designed to help professionals identify and pursue the most in-demand job skills. Since 2018, CourseCompare has helped more than 500,000 people worldwide pursue new digital skills or launch new careers in business, technology, and design. </p>



<p>To compile its annual rankings for Best Coding Bootcamp, CourseCompare focused on job placement rates as a key metric, while also considering the following performance metrics:</p>



<ul><li>Verified ratings from recent graduates</li><li>Industry recognition and satisfaction from employer feedback</li><li>Graduate earning potential, based on salaries within six months of graduation</li><li>Graduation rates taken from a variety of regulatory sources</li></ul>



<p>“We interviewed bootcamp founders and recent graduates, pored over job placement data, took a deep dive into the curriculum, and toured campuses across the country to determine which coding bootcamps are truly delivering a positive return on investment (ROI) for their students in 2021,” CourseCompare noted on their website.</p>



<h2>What Sets BrainStation Apart</h2>



<p>According to CourseCompare, “BrainStation’s LMS (Learning Management System), Synapse, is among the most sophisticated on offer in Canada. The live online learning platform allows students to attend live lectures, collaborate with other professionals, and get immediate feedback from instructors — wherever they are.”</p>



<p>Professionals from over 90 countries have now taken courses and programs at BrainStation, and we continue to welcome and attract new professionals from around the world. In 2020, we met a surge in demand for online training by introducing over 350 new online live courses in multiple time zones.</p>



