<p>“BrainStation has made me a more confident person and has helped me find what I really want to do with my career path. The culture in the classroom is unlike the culture I&#8217;ve experienced in traditional schooling &#8211; everyone is a lot more supportive of one another and not only focused on their own progression. I learned how to learn quickly and apply quickly &#8211; a lasting skill that will definitely be beneficial in the web dev industry in the long run.” &#8211; <strong>Jessica Kwok</strong></p>



